  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 240ºC/ 220ºC (fan)/ gas 9 then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge and open the packet to let it breathe before cooking</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>chicken breasts</strong> <strong>portions</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1641919513890-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1641919513890-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1641919513890-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1641919513890-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1641919513890-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped chicken</strong> in a large bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> vegetable oil</strong>, <strong>coconut yoghurt</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>garam masala </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>marinated chicken</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>marinated chicken</strong> to a baking tray (use <strong>baking paper</strong> to avoid mess!) and put in the oven for 6-8 min or until the chicken is slightly charred (you'll be cooking this in the curry later!)</p><p>Once done, set aside – this is your <strong>chicken tikka</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1641919518157-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
