          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1641919518157-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is charred, turn the oven down to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>cashew nuts</strong> to a bowl, cover with <strong>boiled water</strong> and set aside for 5-6 min or until softened</p>",
